structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 453, sec. 3, effective July 14, 2000. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 307, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 428, sec. 21, effective July 15, 1994. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 346, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988.
